										<h1 itemprop="headline">Don’t!</h1>
					<h2 itemprop="alternativeHeadline">The secret of self-control.</h2>
					<h3>By <span itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="url" content="http://www.newyorker.com/contributors/jonah-lehrer" > <a href="http://www.newyorker.com/contributors/jonah-lehrer" title="Jonah Lehrer" rel="author" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Jonah Lehrer</span></a></span></h3>					<div class="color-footer social-hover bottomOfPost">
						
